===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|en|enm|abod}}, {{m|ang|abad}}, from {{inh|en|ang|*ābād}}, related to {{m|ang|ābīdan||to abide}}; see ''[[abide]]''. Cognate with {{cog|sco|abade}}, {{m|sco|abaid||abode}}. For the change of vowel, compare ''abode'', preterite of ''abide''.

